State.Description: Fixes a bug where if you have more than 128 actors in the same place they start floating around weirdly. Also fixes bug where NPC lips stop moving when a lot of them are nearby.

State.Name: Address Library for SKSE Plugins
State.Author: meh321
State.Description: Contains header file and a database to make SKSE DLL plugins version independent easily.

State.Name: Assorted mesh fixes
State.Author: wankingSkeever
State.Description: Fixes various issues with vanilla Skyrim meshes that causes them to render incorrectly

State.Name: Better Jumping SE
State.Author: meh321 and z65536
State.Description: Allows to jump while sprinting. Also you can configure jump height multiplier, how many times you can jump (double jump like in action games) . No ESP!

State.Name: Bug Fixes SSE
State.Author: meh321
State.Description: Fixes some bugs with game code. See description for more details on which bugs are fixed.

State.Name: Cathedral - Plants
State.Author: The Community
State.Description: HD Vanilla Plant Textures

State.Name: Classic Enhanced - Vanilla Plus Smoothcam Preset
State.Author: Modd Howard
State.Description: A camera preset for Smoothcam focused entirely on gameplay, sticking close to the vanilla over-the-shoulder camera view.

State.Name: Crash Logger
State.Author: Ryan
State.Description: Generates crash logs when the game Just Works

State.Name: Dialogue Movement Enabler
State.Author: Vermunds
State.Description: Allows you to move around in Dialogue Menus.

State.Name: Dynamic Animation Replacer
State.Author: Felisky
State.Description: This mod dynamically replaces the actors' animations depending on various conditions. Supports most actors, including creatures. Actors and animations added by mods are also supported. No ESP file.

State.Name: ENB Helper SE
State.Author: aers
State.Description: Adds necessary functions to support extra features in ENB for Skyrim Special Edition.

State.Name: Encounter Zones Unlocked SE
State.Author: underthesky and z65536
State.Description: Prevents Skyrim from freezing the level of Encounter Zones (like dungeons) when they are first visited.

State.Name: Enhanced Invisibility

State.Description: SKSE plugin that improves and fixes bugs with Invisibility effects

State.Name: Equip Enchantment Fix
State.Author: SlavicPotato

State.Name: Fix Note icon for SkyUI (SKSE64 plugin)
State.Author: 0xC0000005
State.Description: A SKSE64 plugin that fixes the Letter/Note icon and type for SkyUI.

State.Name: Floating Ash Pile Fix

State.Description: Fix floating ash piles by making them fall down to the ground

State.Name: Horse Stamina HUD - Script-Free
State.Author: Parapets
State.Description: Displays your horse's stamina in the HUD when riding a horse.

State.Description: SKSE plugin that distributes keywords to weapons/armor/magic effects/ingestibles and other items, using config files.

State.Name: Left Hand Rings Modified SE
State.Author: Homercide
State.Description: An updated version of Left Hand Rings by Duggelz.  The biped slot number have been changed for people who had conflict problems using the original mod, along with a bunch of added new features.

State.Name: powerofthree's Tweaks

State.Name: PrivateProfileRedirector SE - Faster game start (INI file cacher)

State.Description:
Make Skyrim always take most of CPU usage

Increase FPS and Prevent suddenly lag caused by other processes

State.Name: Spell Perk Item Distributor (SPID)
State.Author: powerofthree
State.Description: SKSE plugin that can be used to add spells/perks/items/shouts/packages/outfits/keywords/factions to every NPC in the game, using config files.

State.Name: SSE Display Tweaks
State.Author: SlavicPotato
State.Description: All-in-one solution for smooth FPS-unlocked gameplay. Includes a physics fix, borderless fullscreen performance boost, refresh rate control, highly configurable frame rate limiting, various bugfixes and more.

State.Name: Stagger Direction Fix - NG
State.Author: Maxsu and NickaNak
State.Description: Updated Stagger Direction Fix adding support for SSE, AE, and VR in one DLL.

State.Author: Maxsu and NickaNak
State.Description: A skse plugin that fix the character's wrong stagger direction bug when the stagger triggered by spell, shout and range weapon.

State.Name: To Your Face SE - AE - VR
State.Author: underthesky and xILARTH
State.Description: "NPCs will not speak greetings towards the Dragonborn's back. SKSE plugin." --underthesky

State.Name: Unique Map Weather Framework
State.Author: doodlez meh321 parapets

State.Name: Unofficial Material Fix
State.Author: Elzee
State.Description:
Why material bugs need to be fixed?

They will cause wrong footstep sounds or just silence them. 

They will also cause wrong sparks and sounds when weapons or other objects hit on them. 

Which will suddenly break immersion during playing.

State.Description: Swaps the "Quest items cannot be removed..." message for a more descriptive message informing you which quest the item belongs to.

State.Description: This mod improves your MCM configuring expirience.

State.Description: Fixes bugs relating to harvestable objects in Skyrim, including the Flora Respawn Bug, in a performance friendly manner.

State.Name: Wiseman303's Flora Fixes - Revamped

State.Author: pauderek
State.Description: Makes dragons shout with an actual voice instead of a roar.

State.Author: me

Make movement more fluid. Changes in:

1. Idle and Turning

2. Running

3. Normal Attack

4. Power Attack

State.Author: Bergzore
State.Description: New running, sprinting, and jumping animations for male and female to look more natural. A must-have mod! These have to be the smoothest jog & sprint animations (to me) because they are very realistic! I have tried them all, trust me! Even the underdogs. I'll say, this one cuts the cake. Check it out!

State.Name: Sound Hammering Sounds
State.Author: sialivi
State.Description: NPCs performing house repairs or maintenance on the mast of a ship will no longer make the sound of hammering on metal. Instead it will make an appropriate wooden sound.

State.Description: New swimming animation!!

State.Name: Whiterun texture memory usage reduction
State.Author: DDVIL
State.Description: A mod that fixes a texture duplicate in Whiterun. Spares VRAM utilization. When using 4k textures, anything helps.

State.Name: Better Animal Footsteps
State.Author: Volnaiskra
State.Description: Tired of being startled by loud footsteps behind you, only to turn around to a little bunny? Ever thought that the hooves of a massive elk should make significantly more noise than the soft paws of a tiny fox? Ever wondered why the spiders sound like they're tapdancing?

State.Name: Better Horse Pain Sounds
State.Author: Yuatari
State.Description: Changes the current horse pain sounds into more bearable versions.
